title: It’s so good, wdym-
text: I see many people on reviews getting mad because of the many updates during events, at first I wasn’t very fond of it but honestly- playing the same map over and over again and no new characters in boring! I love the events they put out every time because it motivates me to grind on the game and work to get the characters. On the old version however, the main goal was just to get a high score, now I have multiple goals or achieve! So overall, it’s a good game and if you’re good with change every month or so then download it, I recommend it highly! Thanks for keeping me entertained subway surfers 😁
